---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — FlightBaggageRules.com"
  description="Privacy policy for FlightBaggageRules.com. Learn how we collect, use, and protect your information."
>
  <div class="container-page py-12">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-display-lg mb-4" style="color:var(--color-ink)">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="text-xs mb-6" style="color:var(--color-mute)">Last updated: June 1, 2026</p>

    <div class="space-y-5 text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color:var(--color-body)">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm mb-3" style="color:var(--color-ink)">1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>FlightBaggageRules.com does not require user registration or collect personal information such as names, emails, or payment details. We may collect:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Anonymous usage data (pages visited, time spent, device type)</li>
          <li>Browser type, language preference, and operating system</li>
          <li>IP address (anonymized for analytics purposes)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm mb-3" style="color:var(--color-ink)">2. How We Use Information</h2>
        <p>We use collected data solely to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 mt-2 space-y-1">
          <li>Improve site performance and content accuracy</li>
          <li>Understand which pages and features are most useful</li>
          <li>Diagnose technical issues</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm mb-3" style="color:var(--color-ink)">3. Cookies</h2>
        <p>We use essential cookies to remember your theme preference (light/dark mode). Third-party analytics tools may set their own cookies. You can disable cookies in your browser settings at any time.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm mb-3" style="color:var(--color-ink)">4. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>We may use third-party services such as analytics providers. These services have their own privacy policies and may collect information as described in their respective policies.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm mb-3" style="color:var(--color-ink)">5. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We do not store personal data on our servers. All analytics data is processed by trusted third-party providers with appropriate security measures in place.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm mb-3" style="color:var(--color-ink)">6. External Links</h2>
        <p>Our site contains links to airline websites and other external resources. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these external sites. We encourage you to review their privacy policies.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm mb-3" style="color:var(--color-ink)">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-display-sm mb-3" style="color:var(--color-ink)">8. Contact</h2>
        <p>If you have questions about this privacy policy, please contact us at <span style="color:var(--color-ink);font-weight:500">privacy@flightbaggagerules.com</span>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
